      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;keycloak-workshop-part-2---hands-on-setup--core-concepts&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Keycloak Workshop: Part 2 - Hands-On Setup &amp;amp; Core Concepts&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#keycloak-workshop-part-2---hands-on-setup--core-concepts&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Excellent! This is a great foundation for Part 2 of your Keycloak workshop. Let me help you expand this into a comprehensive lesson structure.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Major Topics&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;What is Keycloak?&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;How to install&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Keycloak realms, users, &amp;amp; groups&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Clients &amp;amp; Roles&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Protocol mappers &amp;amp; scopes&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Intro to IdPs and more ..&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;keycloak-workshop-part-2---setup--core-concepts&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Keycloak Workshop: Part 2 - Setup &amp;amp; Core Concepts&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#keycloak-workshop-part-2---setup--core-concepts&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;workshop-overview&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Workshop Overview&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#workshop-overview&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;In this session, we&amp;rsquo;ll move from theory to practice by setting up Keycloak and exploring its fundamental components through hands-on exercises.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
